&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">&lt;strong>Reprisal&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Role action. Reduces damage dealt by all enemies in a 5y circle around you by 10% for 15 seconds. 60 second cooldown.&lt;/td>
